{
  "stem": "6777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've seen one of the Germans throwing a grenade into such a little bunker and people climbing out there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I can still remember as-- as if I've seen it, a boy about six, seven, maybe eight years coming out of this with his hair on fire, the face half burned off, hair's on fire.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he still walked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And behind him, other people walking out of the bunker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this I've seen from the window of the first floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they marched all the people to waiting trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some, who wouldn't go quickly enough, they got shot straightaway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, some of us have been kept back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the work was finished, we've been taken on a truck and put into the SS and Gestapo building in Zelazna Street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was really the headquarters of the SS administration of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what it really was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They've put us there in a cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we've been there for, oh, three or four nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got fed a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the final direction comes that the ghetto will not have any more, not even a small number, of people left, that it is a final solution-- because of the resistance, they have decided to finish it off altogether, quickly.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We've been taken to the Polish jail, to the Pawiak, very well known.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And towards the end of the day, some more people have been loaded on the truck and taken to Umshclag, Umshclagplatz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a railway, end of the railway, which, taking the wagons, the trains, to the different camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Down, under.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I've seen it from the windows because-- during the first day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were loaded into a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
